title: Platin V main Mid LFT
body:
Whats up Ladys and Gentleman. This is 5k LoCo and i am currently looking for a team as Main Mid.

I am playing League of Legends since the beta now and got a lot of experience. 
I am currently Plat V and i'd preffer, if the allover ELO is Platin V or higher.
I am from germany and 18 Years old. i am searching for a team 17+ and from germany. if not, i can speak english fluently so thats no problem
